61695]},"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"content":"We have maybe a dozen members if we're lucky. But we are connected to other small communities of similar size up to maybe 3000 members at the largest churches. So we could federate with them to cover a city wide network. Then we'd also probably federate with the global Food Not Bombs network which acts as a multiplier to the whole (about 500 groups internationally). We would probably cover ~5M members just through that.","timestamp":"2026-03-07T14:40:38.910000+00:00","edited_timestamp":"2026-03-07T14:40:55.588000+00:00","tts":false,"mention_everyone":false,"mentions":[],"attachments":[],"embeds":[],"pinned":false,"type":0,"flags":0,"components":[],"position":14,"userName":"xorsense"},{"id":"1479850166256271361","channel_id":"1479847590035062825","author":{"id":"1470753607325450271","username":"ymsvz","avatar":"22cca898691daf0b00d0d176406875d4","discriminator":"0","public_flags":0,"flags":0,"banner":null,"accent_color":null,"global_name":"YMSVZ","avatar_decoration_data":null,"collectibles":null,"display_name_styles":null,"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"content":"wouldnt that divide production along communities, in essence like nations?","timestamp":"2026-03-07T14:36:13.922000+00:00","edited_timestamp":null,"tts":false,"mention_everyone":false,"mentions":[],"attachments":[],"embeds":[],"pinned":false,"type":0,"flags":0,"components":[],"position":13,"userName":"ymsvz"},{"id":"1479850021678612512","channel_id":"1479847590035062825","author":{"id":"302973705452257281","username":"xorsense","avatar":"cb11971578a5b1dc733875667b838997","discriminator":"0","public_flags":0,"flags":0,"banner":null,"accent_color":null,"global_name":"m3talsmith","avatar_decoration_data":null,"collectibles":null,"display_name_styles":{"font_id":8,"effect_id":3,"colors":[61695]},"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"content":"A community can be like Food Not Bombs - in a city.","timest